articles.title: Local singer Kelvin Tan, winner of 2005 Project Superstar, is married - AsiaOne
articles.description: With the Covid-19 restrictions slowly but surely easing, it seems like wedding bells have started ringing once again. We've had a slew of celebrity engagements and weddings over the last couple of months, and now, congratulations are in order for local visual…
